1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 2=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=I'm Her Husband=

4
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,660
Your status doesn't give you

5
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:51,320
the right to trample lives!

6
00:00:52,070 --> 00:00:53,560
Sharp-tongued.

7
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:55,470
Since you are of no use,

8
00:00:55,790 --> 00:00:57,000
you may go to hell.

9
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,200
Why are you here?

10
00:01:33,590 --> 00:01:35,070
You saved me just now?

11
00:01:36,070 --> 00:01:36,950
Thank you.

12
00:01:39,230 --> 00:01:40,920
(The Frost Seal shifted to her.)

13
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,920
What? It hurts!

14
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,510
(So I can feel what's happening to her.)

15
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,200
She's mine now.

16
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:51,760
Let me go!

17
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,840
How dare you do this
before the Grand Princess?

18
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,120
We'll lose our lives for this!

19
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,590
(Why would the ruler save that healer?)

20
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,310
(Has the ruler's heart stirred for her?)

21
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,950
Put me down.

22
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,920
You think I'm a toy boy.

23
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,920
Aren't you?

24
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:11,750
The Fengwu Bracelet.

25
00:02:14,190 --> 00:02:15,800
How did it end up with you?

26
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,560
The Grand Princess promised
to trade it with me.

27
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:20,150
The Grand Princess

28
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:22,310
doesn't keep her word at all.

29
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,910
You know about this?

30
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,960
This bracelet.

31
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:33,240
I truly need it.

32
00:02:33,470 --> 00:02:34,840
Could you lend it to me?

33
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,750
We can make a deal.

34
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,680
Fine.

35
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:44,750
Then let's do it again.

36
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,400
Again?

37
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:54,120
Why bite me?

38
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,080
Not working.

39
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,120
What about this?

40
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,520
What are you doing?

41
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,400
We are strangers.

42
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,870
Why do you keep toying with me?

43
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,120
I...

44
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,840
I actually shed tears.

45
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,200
Absurd.

46
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,680
(Without the Frost Seal,)

47
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,190
(my power will weaken,)

48
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,240
(and the Curse will strike more often.)

49
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:34,120
(Yet even recreating the scene
changed nothing.)

50
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:35,550
(Could it be)

51
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,190
(that I must kill her?)

52
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:40,420
(Everlasting Joy)

53
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,150
(I went through countless trials)

54
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:46,520
(to find this millennium spirit herb.)

55
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:49,090
(Yan Che, future chief)
(If I offer it to wed Zhaoli,)

56
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:50,750
(she'll be happy, right?)

57
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,280
(Yan Che,)

58
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:55,400
(Ming Yuan)
(I need to borrow your body)

59
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,960
(to deal with Ying Du)

60
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,710
(and reclaim all that was once mine.)

61
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,360
(Ying Du,)

62
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,480
(I'm here.)

63
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,040
I should never have helped that toy boy.

64
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,190
Not only was my good deed unrewarded,

65
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:40,190
but I even offended the Grand Princess.

66
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:42,680
(Wuyue tribe)
A loss-making business.

67
00:04:43,250 --> 00:04:44,110
She deserves it.

68
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:46,070
Wu Zhaoli made a potion
without permission.

69
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:48,070
She must answer to the tribe's laws.

70
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,920
Zhaoli acted under orders.

71
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,680
Even if there was fault,

72
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,430
it wasn't hers alone.

73
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,600
Stop trying to excuse her.

74
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,270
Since she's not present,

75
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,390
as the chief,

76
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,510
(Chief)
I'll punish you.

77
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,430
Blame yourself for lacking discipline.

78
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:05,510
Grandmother!

79
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:06,470
Zhaoli.

80
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,640
Zhaoli.

81
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,110
Grandmother, are you alright?

82
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,430
Zhaoli, why are you back?

83
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:16,270
Go now.

84
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:17,600
I'm responsible for it,

85
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,040
but my grandmother is not.

86
00:05:19,190 --> 00:05:21,270
Since when do we face shared punishment?

87
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:22,720
Uncle.

88
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:24,360
Wu Zhaoli is truly reckless.

89
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,810
(Wu Luoluo, Yan Che's sister)
We answer to the royals.

90
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,830
If the potion she gave
to the Grand Princess

91
00:05:28,841 --> 00:05:29,270
goes wrong,

92
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:30,870
no one can shoulder that burden.

93
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:31,840
Wu Luoluo,

94
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,950
stop stirring up trouble here

95
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,800
by speaking of things
that haven't happened.

96
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:37,110
What?

97
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,750
Are you hoping the tribe

98
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:40,190
will face some misfortune?

99
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:41,950
Have you not heard

100
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:44,830
of shared glory and losses?

101
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,160
How dare you smear her?

102
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:48,800
Haven't you learned any remorse?

103
00:05:50,430 --> 00:05:51,310
Zhaoli.

104
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,320
Zhaoli!

105
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,040
(Just a few lashes hurt this much.)

106
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:58,830
(If she dies,)

107
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,630
(will I feel the same pain?)

108
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,220
(I'll let her live for a few more days.)

109
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:05,040
(I can kill her after she heals.)

110
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:06,310
Do you admit your fault?

111
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,270
I did nothing wrong.

112
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,390
Do you feel any regret?

113
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,560
It's you.

114
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,950
Why have you come again?

115
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,840
Because it hurts.

116
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,520
Uncle.

117
00:06:35,770 --> 00:06:36,720
Zhaoli actually brought

118
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,720
a strange man back!

119
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:39,310
How reckless!

120
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:42,040
How dare an outsider trespass here!

121
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:42,960
Guards!

122
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,120
- Yes.
- Yes.

123
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,750
Seize this outsider.

124
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:46,590
Chief,

125
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:48,390
my mistake has nothing to do with him.

126
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:52,360
I don't care why you've come.

127
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:53,830
Matters of the Wuyue tribe

128
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,480
are none of your concern.

129
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,560
Leave now.

130
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:58,360
(Struggling to protect yourself,)

131
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,120
(you're still trying to protect me?)

132
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:03,870
I'm no outsider.

133
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,400
Honey.

134
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,160
You're the one from my dreams?

135
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:14,510
I am her

136
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,560
husband.

137
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:19,150
What?

138
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,310
Zhaoli is married?

139
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:22,060
What is going on?

140
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,650
What should Yan Che do when he's back?

141
00:07:23,670 --> 00:07:25,900
He's been saying since childhood
that he'd marry Zhaoli.

142
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,260
You belong to the Grand Princess.

143
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,830
Do you even realize what you're saying

144
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:30,240
could get us all killed?

145
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,320
Whether you're Zhaoli's secret lover

146
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,140
or her husband,

147
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:36,440
Zhaoli must face the punishment

148
00:07:36,470 --> 00:07:37,680
for her mistake.

149
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:48,040
This is the Puluo Token.

150
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,830
From this day on,

151
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:51,190
anyone who dares harm her

152
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:53,270
will be standing against me.

153
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,750
Zhaoli found herself a royal backer.

154
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:57,070
That's a powerful support.

155
00:07:57,070 --> 00:07:58,510
Indeed.

156
00:08:06,310 --> 00:08:07,510
Put me down!

157
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:08,630
I can walk on my own.

158
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:12,030
It's here.

159
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,600
Put me down already.

160
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,310
We've arrived.

161
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,750
With such grievous wounds,

162
00:08:29,190 --> 00:08:30,360
why would you still shield me?

163
00:08:32,550 --> 00:08:34,540
I just don't want to drag
the innocent into this.

164
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,510
We've met so many times.

165
00:08:45,790 --> 00:08:47,000
What's your name?

166
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,560
Ying Du.

167
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:51,110
Ying Du?

168
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:56,630
Ying Du,

169
00:08:57,190 --> 00:08:58,030
though I don't know

170
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:59,390
the purpose of your visit,

171
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,150
you just saved my life,

172
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,630
and I truly thank you for that.

173
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,360
However,

174
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:11,150
you're the Grand Princess's toy boy.

175
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,600
Sneaking out could cost you your life.

176
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,300
If you wish to stay safe,

177
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:16,960
you should leave at once.

178
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,110
Otherwise...

179
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:28,880
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

180
00:09:30,710 --> 00:09:35,680
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

181
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:40,420
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

182
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:43,320
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

183
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:49,130
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

184
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:52,830
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

185
00:09:53,180 --> 00:09:55,530
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

186
00:09:55,530 --> 00:09:59,570
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

187
00:09:59,570 --> 00:10:01,950
♪And that is enough♪

188
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:05,740
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

189
00:10:05,950 --> 00:10:08,710
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

190
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:14,830
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

191
